<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَكُنْ فِي هَذِهِ الدُّنْيَا غَرِيبَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَكُنْ عَنْ كُلِّ فَاحِشَةٍ جَبَاناً<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَكُنْ فِي الْخَيْرِ مِقْدَاماً نَجِيبَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلاحِظْ زِينَة الدُّنْيَا بِبُغْضٍ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>تَكُنْ عَبْداً إِلى الْمَوْلَى حَبِيبَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَمَنْ يَخْبُرْ زَخَارِفَهَا يَجِدْهَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مُخَالِبَةً لِطَالِبِهَا خَلُوبَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَغُضَّ عَنِ الْمَحَارِمِ مِنْكَ طَرْفاً<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>طَمُوحاً يَفْتِنُ الرَّجُلَ الأَرِيبَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَخَائِنَةُ الْعُيُونِ كَأُسْدِ غَابٍ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إِذَا مَا أَهْمَلْتَ وَثَبْتَ وَثُوبَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَمَنْ يَغْضُضْ فُضُولَ الطَّرَفِ عَنْهَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>يَجِدْ فِي قَلْبِهِ رُوحاً وَطِيبَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَلا تُطْلِقْ لِسَانَكَ فِي كَلامٍ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>يَجُرُّ عَلَيْكَ أَحْقَاداً وَحُوبَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَلا يَبْرَحْ لِسَانُكَ كُلَّ وَقْتٍ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>بِذِكْرِ اللهِ رَيَّاناً رَطِيبَا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَصَلِّ إِذَا الدُّجَى أَرْخَى سُدُولاً<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَلا تَضْجَرْ بِهِ وَتَكُنْ هَيُوبَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>تَجِدْ أُنْساً إِذَا أُودِعْتَ قَبْراً<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَفَارَقْتَ الْمَعَاشِرُ وَالنَّسِيبَا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>